thread.title: Cindy Lara

author: Cindy Lara
title: Cindy Lara
text: I needed a place close to home, which it is, plus the price was a bit less than other ones. There are also climate controlled ones available if you choose. The only thing I was not aware of was the insurance I have to pay of $9 every month which is added to the cost of the rental making it higher than what I had expected to pay, other than that it appears to be a newer facility so very nice and clean.
